{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"2043","airdate":"1521572400","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona and Slaygon","showname":"TueSIDay with Marcel ","blurb":"Ellou Everyone!\n\nWe're glad to announce our next live show with our guest: Sidologie a.k.a. Marcel Donn\u00e9! He is well-known as the Jean-Michel Jarre of the 64 scene, and now he is going to talk about his early years, his Project Sidologie (both I and II) with the 6+1 CD-s, and maaany more things!\n\nJoin the conversation, ask questions, request songs, and \nSLAY tuned!\n","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona and Slaygon<\/big><\/strong><br \/>TueSIDay with Marcel ","nice_airdate":"Tuesday 20th March, 2018<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2044","airdate":"1521658800","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Bozzy and the Bint","showname":"BBKB","blurb":"It's the Taint of the Week\u2122 so it's time to listen to Boz to talk utter bollocks in between your requests. Unfortunately Kate isn't here to translate some of it into English, so you're going to have to listen intently! All aboard the Train-Wreck, WOO WOOH!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Bozzy and the Bint<\/big><\/strong><br \/>BBKB","nice_airdate":"Wednesday 21st March, 2018<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2045","airdate":"1521745200","name_switch":"off","DJ":"KraxxUltima","showname":"Krax plays Trax again indeed","blurb":"Ahoy everyone and welcome aboard once more for another hearty voyage over the Commodore oceans. Request your favorite C64\/Amiga tunes and your courageous captain shall play them to the best of capabilities. Damn the torpedoes and let's blast =)","nice_showname":"<strong><big>KraxxUltima<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Krax plays Trax again indeed","nice_airdate":"Thursday 22nd March, 2018<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"}]}